|----------|---------|
| `fetchDocument(id)` | Retrieves a document by ID from the database |
| `createDocument(data)` | Creates a new document with the provided data |
| `validateDocument(doc)` | Validates that the document has required title and content |
| `updateDocument(id, data)` | Updates an existing document with partial data |

